originalText.text:
I have been coming to Dr. Low for quite a few years now, and always have a great experience. I am always nervous about my dental issues, and Dr Low takes the time to explain things and put my mind to ease, before beginning any work on my teeth. When I have an emergency situation, she gets me in right away, does the procedure, and then follows up to see how I am doing.  I have had cleanings, fillings, root canals, and implants done here over the years, because I trust her expertise. She is more concerned about the patient feeling better, than she is about getting paid for the dental work.
I can't say enough good things about her. I am in good hands when I need dental work done, and I won't go to anyone else.
